    "en": {
      "title": "Knife catcher killed by cobra attack",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ambalangoda police say that yesterday (25th), a knife catcher who carried the captured knife in the forest and put it on display died in a knife attack.",
        "The police say that a father of four named Sudath Kumara, a resident of Ambalangoda Akurala, has died.",
        "The villagers said that the dead man had caught a Naya who had come to a house in Akurala and while holding the naya on his shoulders, he was being attacked while holding the naya by both hands and pulling him to and fro.",
        "Police say that the person who was attacked by Nai was first transferred to Balapitiya Hospital and then to Karapitiya Hospital and he died while receiving treatment at Karapitiya Hospital for four days.",
        "Locals say that the person who died from snake venom had caught many snakes and released them into the wild."
      ],
